snippet: Nick Calathes, subbing for an injured Mike Conley, scored a career-high 22 points and the surging Memphis Grizzlies defeated the Milwaukee Bucks 99-90 on Saturday night....

headline.print_headline: Calathes Scores 22 as Grizzlies Beat Bucks 99-90
headline.main: Calathes Scores 22 as Grizzlies Beat Bucks 99-90

lead_paragraph: Nick Calathes, subbing for an injured Mike Conley, scored a career-high 22 points and the surging Memphis Grizzlies defeated the Milwaukee Bucks 99-90 on Saturday night.
